Maxi-Man
The Maxi-Man is the result of extreme physical augmentation: a human body
pushed to its absolute limits through nano-augmentation, bio-enhancement,
and relentless physical conditioning. Maxi-Men are among the most physically
powerful humans on Rifts Earth.

ATTRIBUTE REQUIREMENTS
  Physical Strength (PS):    12 minimum
  Physical Endurance (PE):   12 minimum
  Speed (SPD):               10 minimum

BASE SKILLS
  Boxing (trained)
  Body Building (trained)
  Running (trained)
  Athletics
  Acrobatics (65%)
  Gymnastics (60%)
  Climbing (55%)
  Swimming (60%)
  W.P. Knife
  W.P. Energy Rifle
  Hand-to-Hand: Commando

OCC SKILLS (5 picks from)
  Physical, Military, Espionage, W.P.

SECONDARY SKILLS
  4 picks from any category

SPECIAL ABILITIES
  Nano-augmentation grants enhanced physical performance. The Maxi-Man's
  natural PS is treated as Augmented PS for damage bonus purposes.
  At higher levels, natural healing rates exceed human norms.

STARTING EQUIPMENT
  Environmental body armor, vibro-knife, CP-30 laser pistol, energy clip,
  3d6x100 credits.

HP PER LEVEL: 2d6

